LIRC kernel modules source for DEBIAN
=====================================

In the Debian packaging of LIRC, kernel module sources are installed in
/usr/src/lirc-modules.tar.gz. In order to build them, you should use
module-assistant and run:

m-a prepare # to prepare your system to build modules for the current kernel
m-a install lirc # to build a .deb of the lirc modules and install it

Please read the module-assistant docs for more information.

